query:
INSERT INTO ohlcv (symbol, date, open, high, low, close, volume, source)
                VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8)
                ON CONFLICT (symbol, date, source) 
                DO UPDATE SET 
                    open = EXCLUDED.open,
                    high = EXCLUDED.high,
                    low = EXCLUDED.low,
                    close = EXCLUDED.close,
                    volume = EXCLUDED.volume
